# data/: the SQLite archive is NO LONGER committed to main (2026-07-23). The
# 84MB binary lived on main and was re-committed every run — bloating history +
# causing recurring binary merge conflicts on every PR. It now lives on the
# orphan `data` branch (single-commit snapshot, force-pushed each run); the
# pipeline restores it at job start and persists it back there. main is code
# only. See docs/DATA_BRANCH.md.
data/

